WEBVTT

00:00:28.567 --> 00:00:31.625
the bomber and I, unknowingly,

00:00:31.649 --> 00:00:36.196
boarded the same train carriage
at the same time,

00:00:36.220 --> 00:00:40.683
standing, apparently, just feet apart.

00:00:42.345 --> 00:00:43.495
I didn't see him.

00:00:44.185 --> 00:00:45.976
Actually, I didn't see anyone.

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:48.587
You know not to look
at anyone on the Tube,

00:00:48.611 --> 00:00:51.912
but I guess he saw me.

00:00:52.916 --> 00:00:55.957
I guess he looked at all of us,

00:00:56.687 --> 00:01:00.901
as his hand hovered
over the detonation switch.